text: Joel Murray (born April 17, 1963 in Wilmette, Illinois) is an American actor. He has starred many television shows including Grand, Love & War, and Dharma and Greg. He also performed in movies, including God Bless America, Monsters University and Killing Reagan. His brothers are actor/comedian Bill Murray and Brian Doyle-Murray. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Illinois
